WEBVTT

00:00:04.400 --> 00:00:06.610 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When I was 17 years old,

00:00:06.610 --> 00:00:09.822 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I was very shy and had low self-esteem.

00:00:09.822 --> 00:00:12.700 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Almost all my classmates had girlfriends

00:00:12.700 --> 00:00:14.827 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and looked like they were having fun.

00:00:14.827 --> 00:00:17.496 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This made me feel really lonely.

00:00:17.496 --> 00:00:20.082 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I had been baptized for four years.

00:00:20.082 --> 00:00:23.711 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
At school, my classmates respected me

00:00:23.711 --> 00:00:25.421 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
because of my conduct.

00:00:25.421 --> 00:00:26.922 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But something was about to happen

00:00:26.922 --> 00:00:30.259 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that could have changed my life forever.

00:00:30.259 --> 00:00:31.886 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
There were a lot of girls at my school.

00:00:31.886 --> 00:00:35.598 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
One girl in particular was really pretty.

00:00:35.598 --> 00:00:38.017 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Although we were not in the same class,

00:00:38.017 --> 00:00:41.186 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we would often see each other in the hall,

00:00:41.186 --> 00:00:43.063 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in the school cafeteria,

00:00:43.063 --> 00:00:45.065 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
or during gym class.

00:00:45.065 --> 00:00:47.651 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I noticed that she would look at me.

00:00:47.651 --> 00:00:52.656 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
One day,
two girls handed me a letter from her.

00:00:52.656 --> 00:00:54.658 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The letter said:

00:00:54.658 --> 00:00:57.119 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“I think we would get along.

00:00:57.119 --> 00:00:58.662 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“I’m attracted to you.

00:00:58.662 --> 00:01:00.205 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“I like your personality,

00:01:00.205 --> 00:01:01.874 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“and that’s not all.

00:01:01.874 --> 00:01:04.126 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“I hope you make the right decision.

00:01:04.126 --> 00:01:06.462 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“We could really have fun together.

00:01:06.462 --> 00:01:08.756 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With love, yours truly.”

00:01:08.756 --> 00:01:13.052 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I felt dazed;
I honestly didn’t know what to do.

00:01:13.052 --> 00:01:17.431 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
My classmates urged me
to accept her proposition immediately.

00:01:17.431 --> 00:01:19.475 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When I got home,

00:01:19.475 --> 00:01:21.101 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I was really confused.

00:01:21.101 --> 00:01:24.063 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
My parents asked me what was going on,

00:01:24.063 --> 00:01:26.482 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but I couldn’t talk to them about it.

00:01:28.025 --> 00:01:33.030 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I wondered whether I would ever meet
another girl as beautiful as she was.

00:01:33.822 --> 00:01:38.369 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
During those days,
it was as if I had lost my Christian identity.

00:01:38.369 --> 00:01:40.412 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I prayed a lot.

00:01:40.412 --> 00:01:44.541 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I had dedicated my life to Jehovah,
and I couldn’t let him down.

00:01:44.541 --> 00:01:46.418 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So I opened up to my parents,

00:01:46.418 --> 00:01:49.421 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and they were patient with me.

00:01:49.421 --> 00:01:53.592 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We did some intensive study together,
using the Young People Ask book.

00:01:53.592 --> 00:01:57.638 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Going through articles
that applied to me helped me

00:01:57.638 --> 00:01:59.306 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
overcome the problem.

00:01:59.306 --> 00:02:03.018 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I also spoke to a mature brother
in the congregation

00:02:03.018 --> 00:02:05.145 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and decided to spend more time with him

00:02:05.145 --> 00:02:07.815 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
as well as other brothers.

00:02:07.815 --> 00:02:08.983 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I mustered up courage.

00:02:08.983 --> 00:02:12.236 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I went to her and told her my decision.

00:02:13.404 --> 00:02:15.823 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I explained my Bible-based convictions

00:02:15.823 --> 00:02:18.033 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and said no.

00:02:18.033 --> 00:02:20.744 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It was a very wise decision.

00:02:20.744 --> 00:02:23.288 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I then had a clean conscience,

00:02:23.288 --> 00:02:25.958 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and I hadn’t brought reproach
on Jehovah’s name.

00:02:26.500 --> 00:02:29.003 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I had safeguarded my relationship with him.

00:02:29.003 --> 00:02:33.465 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I learned that if we are determined
to be loyal to Jehovah

00:02:33.465 --> 00:02:36.343 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and we have the courage
to remain chaste, well,

00:02:36.343 --> 00:02:38.429 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we won’t have any regrets.

00:02:38.429 --> 00:02:42.307 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Until age 17,
I had not understood this.

00:02:42.307 --> 00:02:45.561 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah has truly blessed me since then,

00:02:45.561 --> 00:02:48.856 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
giving me the privilege of serving
in the congregation in many ways

00:02:48.856 --> 00:02:51.734 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and giving me a lovely wife
to serve him with.

00:02:51.734 --> 00:02:56.739 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I thank Jehovah for having helped me
to make the right decision.

